ogleSignInPlugin plugin = GoogleSignInPlatform.instance as web.GoogleSignInPlugin;\\n    \\n    return plugin.renderButton(\\n      configuration: web.GSIButtonConfiguration(\\n        type: web.GSIButtonType.standard,\\n        shape: web.GSIButtonShape.rectangular,\\n        theme: web.GSIButtonTheme.outline,\\n      ),\\n    );\\n  } else {\\n    // Return your mobile/desktop sign-in bu\\n\u003ctruncated 183 bytes\u003e\\n Events**: Since `renderButton()` handles the UI, you should listen to `GoogleSignIn.instance.authenticationEvents` to handle the result of the sign-in flow (e.g., updating your app's state when a user successfully signs in)[1][2].\\n*   **Authorized Origins**: Ensure your `index.html` contains the correct `google-signin-client_id` meta tag, and that your Google Cloud Console project has your web URL (e.g., `http://localhost:7357`) added to the **Authorized JavaScript origins**[1].\\n*   **Token Refresh**: On the web, the `accessToken` does not automatically refresh[1][2]. Your application must be prepared to handle expired tokens and re-trigger authentication flows if necessary[1][2].\\n\\nSources:\\n[1] [pub.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHnbCULCreIb_TguFz_1skCS1bD6hvgHbdJ9GvFk0lNMckzd26rEPXA4FgKtdw4YBCzjPODlyr2mdhGLa7xQ-mAOPqq7tifJvValrHJB9tpH5OTXa33VZU16U5JmKMZEc8WAGdupIWw8RhNJVvPC2zbGHl7)\\n[2] [pub.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEqaABG69o0377TcKZZsTTVcOUFfaI_FCHUFzAQxMqTiQDsBo8CJ0nI6gQnhR2kX_-4oe7X3AttA-B1NqZ0cdWp_xCoyuraCDvmOl2B0XSDRRQFJ4cHqV8F-thq4XQL-WbQnQ==)\\n[3] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF4kZ8783LyXBQFLd2FpimJxLSEGaKuwVUCPH8WYxFWhlbMq7eQNAFEY74jW0hOGBU5rstrjaK9Sc9PGU_3PGfEJdbfnb4zDx3D7SBmWiGTgar-FIs49Qmzk1KvK3nytLBZxIjwj1LIn1nJUv_eY-d6kODsGX49bwUJULDfEiNi3vWsjrLj6W0Wx9UOlapXRMBMX9_xXnospGeSxRlf-8VPSO1VIx2YwTQdHFaddmD-iq7ht7PaUw==)\\n[4] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.co