### Step 4: Redesign the Bottom Navigation Bar with Centered Cradle FAB
Modify the outer Scaffold inside `collection_view.dart` (`_CollectionViewState.build`) around lines 610-695:

1. **Configure the Notched `BottomAppBar` & Central FAB:**
```dart
      floatingActionButtonLocation: FloatingActionButtonLocation.centerDocked,
      floatingActionButton: FloatingActionButton(
        backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF6B1524),
        foregroundColor: Colors.white,
        elevation: 4,
        shape: const CircleBorder(side: BorderSide(color: Color(0xFFE5C158), width: 1.5)),
        child: Icon(_currentTabIndex == 0 ? Icons.swap_horiz : Icons.today, size: 28),
        onPressed: () {
          if (_currentTabIndex == 0) {
            // Patients Tab: Toggle search landing page vs. list view
            final dbState = _dbKeys[_currentTabIndex].currentState;
            if (dbState != null) {
              setState(() {
                dbState.toggleLandingPage(); // Custom method to invert _showLandingPage
              });
            }
          } else {
            // Reports Tab: Instantly generate Daily report for Today!
            _generateDailyReportForToday();
          }
        },
